{"tid":381751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"隔牆有耳： 立會天書勁賺　吳文華搞社企","createTime":"2017-08-31T08:11:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T08:11:46.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"03e9c3365b3c27299e0879dab17e381a910276a7","tid":381751,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:11:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170831/20137838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170831%2F20137838&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=fb40dc7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170831%2F20137838&h=a36ef1ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170831/20137838</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：<br />\n立會天書勁賺　吳文華搞社企<br />\n<br />\n3,254<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170831/large/15677930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170831%2Flarge%2F15677930.jpg&h=a85fb7a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■吳文華<br />\n資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n立法會前秘書長吳文華（Pauline）舊年曾為立法會完成俗稱「議會天書」嘅《香港特別行政區立法會歷史、規則及行事方式參考手冊》，佢噚日出席一個公開活動時自爆，幫立法會寫書4年，總共賺咗超過200萬，即係人工平均一年超過50萬元，佢就用咗呢筆錢成立社企，聘請殘疾人士設立名為「<a href=\"http://We60.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWe60.com&d=%2FNfhDC2D30LZjaqxolDEFf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=96e8df25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://We60.com</a>」嘅平台，希望可以協助踏入60歲嘅人士，更多參與社會工作。<br />\nPauline又慨嘆，近年立法會立立亂，「因為冇人睇我本書，如果唔係唔會搞成咁」，但好慶幸自己嗰本書，法庭成日都引用，「已成為最可靠同有權威嘅文獻」，當然佢最開心係可以寫番立法會歷史出嚟啦！  <br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n隔牆有耳：林正財唔認老　話年輕人萎縮 (李八方)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n隔牆有耳： 帶埋三局長　娥特又北上 (李八方)"}]}